snippet.title: tic tac toe - SPEED TAPPING  (iPhone/Android GAME APPs)
snippet.description:
URL▶ https://tictactoe-speedtapping.amebaownd.com/


Tic-tac-toe in a game of speed!
The one with the fastest tap and the smartest brain wins!

The basic rules are the same as in tic-tac-toe.
The difference is the way the block is taken.
・Tap three times to get a block.
 　Tap quickly to get it.
・Lose it, try to get it back!
・Vertical, Horizontal, or Diagonal, get any one row, you win!

With friends, parents-child, family, one phone two players!
-------------------------------
- STYLE -
It's a phone game, but it's  play face to face, in real life.

- FUN -
Children loves slapstick, tap-tap, in every era.
Let's be as tap as you like!

"Children's trait" x "Ancient classic games" x "Actions unique to phones"
= [ The super new classic game ! ] 

- OVERVIEW -
Age:3+
Players:1-2
Genre:Board games, Table games.
